{{Infobox Officeholder | name = Stanislav Todorov Stanilov | image = |country = {{BUL}} | office1 = | term_start1 = | term_end1 = |birth_date = {{birth date and age|1943|09|09|df=y}} |birth_place = [[Gabrovo]], [[People's Republic of Bulgaria|Bulgaria]] |party = |spouse = |partner = |children = |profession = [[Politician]], [[Historian]], [[Archaeologist]] |religion = |nationality = [[Bulgarian nationality law|Bulgarian]] }}
'''Stanislav Stanilov''' ([[Bulgarian language|Bulgarian]]: Станислав Станилов), (born 9 September 1943, in [[Gabrovo]]) is a [[Bulgaria]]n [[archaeologist]], [[historian]] and [[politician]].<ref>{{cite web|last= |first= |url=http://www.parliament.bg/bg/MP/1061|title=Профил на Станислав Станилов|publisher=National Parliament of Bulgaria official website |date=2013 |accessdate=2014-09-20}}</ref> Stanilov has been a member of the [[Attack (political party)|Attack]] since its founding in 2005 and became vice-chairman of its parliamentary group on 13 November 2007,<ref>{{cite web|last= |first= |url=http://www.omda.bg/page.php?IDMenu=386&IDArticle=854|title=Атака|publisher=omda.bg |date=2012-01-17 |accessdate=2014-09-24}}</ref> a position which he still retains.<ref>{{cite web|last= |first= |url=http://www.mediapool.bg/ataka-ne-podkrepyala-pravitelstvoto-a-rabotata-na-parlamenta-news220895.html|title="Атака" не подкрепяла правителството, а работата на парламента|publisher=mediapool.bg |date=2014-05-30 |accessdate=2014-09-24}}</ref> In addition to his native Bulgarian, Stanilov is fluent in [[Russian language|Russian]] and [[German language|German]].<ref>{{cite web|last= |first= |url=http://www.vestnikataka.com/?module=displaystory&story_id=72806&format=print|title=Проф. Станислав Станилов, зам.-председател на ПГ АТАКА: напъните на шефа на СКАТ да прави партия са фарс|publisher=vestnikataka.com|date=2010-01-12 |accessdate=2014-09-24}}</ref>
